[00:04.06]It's too small.|它太小了。
[00:07.33]Listen to the tape then answer this question.|先听这段录音，然后再回答这个问题。
[00:13.35]What kind of dress does the Lady want?|这位女士想要什么样的裙子呢？
[00:19.27]Do you like this dress, madam?|夫人，您喜欢这条裙子吗？
[00:23.43]I like the colour very much.|我非常喜欢这个颜色。
[00:27.07]It's a lovely dress, but it's too small for me.|这条裙子很漂亮，不过对我来说太小了。
[00:33.33]What about this one?|这个怎么样？
[00:35.78]It's a lovely dress.|这是一条非常漂亮的裙子。
[00:38.40]It's very smart.|它非常聪明。
[00:40.98]Short skirts are in fashion now.|短裙现在很流行。
[00:44.68]Would you like to try it?|你想试试吗？
[00:47.67]All right.|好的。
[00:49.82]I'm afraid this green dress is too small for me as well.|恐怕这条绿色的裙子对我来说也太小了。
